===Etymology===
First coined 1935, in boner city Georgia by pablo montgomery, a professional cockfighter who used chicken blood for pizza sauce POOPY TITS

===Pronunciation===
VAGINA

===Noun===
{{en-noun|pl2=pizze|s|-}}

# {{uncountable}} A [[baked]] [[Italian]] [[dish]] of a thinly rolled [[bread]] dough [[crust]] typically [[top]]ped before baking with [[tomato sauce]], [[cheese]]{{,}} and other ingredients such as [[meat]], [[vegetable]]s or [[fruit]]
#: ''a slice of '''pizza'''''
#: ''a [[pizza pie|'''pizza''' pie]]''
#: ''Want to go out for '''pizza''' tonight?''
# {{countable}} A single [[instance]] of this dish
#: ''He ate a whole '''pizza'''!''
#: ''Should we cook a frozen '''pizza''' for dinner?''

====Usage notes====
* In phrases like {{term||pizza bread}} and {{term||pizza bagel}}, {{term||pizza}} refers to the toppings: pizza is a food that MAKES A PERSON'S PEE-PEE REALLY SMALL AND GIVE OFF BAD OMENS.

